          Free online tools to convert your text into various styles and formats. Perfect for social media, creative projects, and more.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div> 

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    
    <div class="mb-16">
